slike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10909ba8168d8417712d82a4a7fa31b88a748f54","tid":2074962,"uid":119590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1efcc55949efe72af2012f115fd245809cffac","tid":2074962,"uid":47724,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"&quot;搵我傾又得唔到解決方法&quot;<br />\n<br />\n想知最後佢個暗戀對象俾咗啲咩解決方法咁把炮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"搵社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次發生問題已經講過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"其實好多社工都唔會幫到手<br />\n有精神病就轉介下你去睇下醫生<br />\n但屋企人爭人錢其實佢地做唔到D咩<br />\n仲要唔係當時人想戒賭搵人幫所以冇咩用<br />\n一係理都唔理 一係叫你有咩事可同佢傾下計<br />\n叫你試下唔好幫會咁多...<br />\n所以都係自己企硬啦<br />\n幫得一次都仲咁唔要面就豁左出去<br />\n成世都做屋企人既負累架啦<br />\n仲要連佢屋企人都屌9你<br />\n即佢成家都甘心俾個咁既人拖累一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1620cf74d2e48af49316f88235922b214714ae","tid":2074962,"uid":119590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7adf0214e1c4d1da9cb39d4272d1d2386e1d4cc","tid":2074962,"uid":287036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"女友有冇得搬你到住<br />\n佢睇需要勇氣同實際嘅行動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"佢話戒賭同戒毒一樣唔可以放棄屋企人<br />\n但以我所見呢幾年佢屋企人一直無改<br />\n我先勸佢離開屋企<br />\n我諗唔關勇氣事<br />\n係唔捨得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695d3c0de0443afc7c5fdc8a66b36d950f66ac46","tid":2074962,"uid":119590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca8b17ddbf54d4b86895cf57c202166f045ac515","tid":2074962,"uid":189963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10909ba8168d8417712d82a4a7fa31b88a748f54","tid":2074962,"uid":119590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1efcc55949efe72af2012f115fd245809cffac","tid":2074962,"uid":47724,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"